haReport:
This mission was flown by:
Kmdr Patrik Schorner
Ltn Augustus Kass
Fw Gebhard Schonbaum
Fw Ruprecht Hess

 The mission was flown from Balatre aerodrome.

Successes include the following: 
On 03/09/1916 near Suippes.
A F.E.2b of Esc 19 was brought down by Nikolaus Schildhauer of Jasta 16b.
Sergt Edmond Lafitte was killed in action.
S/Lt Pierre Maigron was killed in action.
Nikolaus Schildhauer was  flying a Halberstadt D.II.

On 03/09/1916 near Witry-les-Reims.
A Nieuport 17.C1 of Esc N.67 was brought down by Wolfram Tendler of Jasta 16b.
Sergt Andre Gentillon was killed in action.
Wolfram Tendler was  flying a Halberstadt D.II.

On 03/09/1916 near Malancourt.
A F.E.2b of Esc 17 was brought down by Rupert Freudenberg of Jasta 16b.
Lt Cyrille Lacaze was killed in action.
Lt Geraud Mordant was killed in action.
Rupert Freudenberg was  flying a Halberstadt D.II.
